{"id": "1414124730923094057", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "943711292160634901", "author_name": "yecun7302", "author_bot": false, "content": "始めたばかりの初心者です。ケティグーラというキャラのおすすめ編成をどなたか教えていただきたいです。", "timestamp": "2025-09-07T05:46:49.019000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1414141097034387548", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "現在復刻中のハーメルンとオルラはそれぞれ強力なサポートでケティグーラも恩恵を受けやすいキャラたちなので余裕があるなら引いておくといいと思います", "timestamp": "2025-09-07T06:51:51.004000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1414141725815079032", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "とはいえケティグーラの排出期間は今日までなのでケティグーラが3凸未満であれば凸を進めることをおすすめします", "timestamp": "2025-09-07T06:54:20.917000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-07T06:55:07.760000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1414143890696441876", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "懐事情を推し量るのは難しいので、あくまで自分ならこうするという話であれば、ケティグーラ可能な限り凸→22日までにハーメルン確保→（余裕があれば追加でオルラ確保+ハーメルン凸）→22日から復刻のライカー確保といった感じでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2025-09-07T07:02:57.065000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1414144063241719909", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512499694346305536", "author_name": "eyu17", "author_bot": false, "content": "もちろんケティグーラを強く使いたいという前提ありきですが", "timestamp": "2025-09-07T07:03:38.203000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
